{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spring Tales welcomes you to Blossomdale a cozy town where the community is coming together to prepare for a spring festival after a devastating storm. The festival isn\u2019t just a celebration of the new season, it\u2019s a way for the townspeople to heal, rebuild, and lift each other\u2019s spirits. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/extras/FixingStreetlightgif-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1736412564\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019ll follow the lives of five unique characters as they navigate the challenges of recovery and festival preparation. You\u2019ll help them solve puzzles and discover their stories along the way. It\u2019s a game about friendship, teamwork, and the simple joys of coming together after hard times. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/extras/damage-to-normal-optimize.gif?t=1736412564\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With its warm atmosphere and charming hand-drawn visuals, Spring Tales offers a relaxing and heartfelt experience perfect for unwinding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/extras/CleaningManhole-optimize.gif?t=1736412564\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Follow the lives of five characters, each with their own story and role in the festival.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy the hand-drawn visuals that bring the town and its people to life.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Solve puzzles that are woven into the story and help the characters on their journey.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take a break and immerse yourself in the calming, cozy world of Blossomdale.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the warmth of a community coming together to rebuild, heal, and celebrate after a storm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736412564","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736412564","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/9e75f3896a26d076caf9c236a9efbb32b8235a34/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736412564","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/9e75f3896a26d076caf9c236a9efbb32b8235a34/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736412564","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spring Tales welcomes you to Blossomdale a cozy town where the community is coming together to prepare for a spring festival after a devastating storm. The festival isn\u2019t just a celebration of the new season, it\u2019s a way for the townspeople to heal, rebuild, and lift each other\u2019s spirits. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194840/extras/FixingStreetlightgif-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1736412564\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019ll follow the lives of five unique characters as they navigate the challenges of recovery and festival preparation. You\u2019ll help them solve puzzles and discover their stories along the way. It\u2019s a game about friendship, teamwork, and the simple joys of coming together after hard times. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamsta